REFORM; CIVIC FORUM (ORGANIZATION); CZECHOSLOVAKIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; 
RESIGNATIONS; DISSIDENTS -- CZECHOSLOVAKIA; CARNOGURSKY, JAN; CALFA, MARIAN; 
ADAMEC, LADISLAV 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
