<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Hank Aaron, baseball's all-time home run leader, has been promoted to senior 
vice president of the Atlanta Braves. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
AARON, HENRY; ATLANTA BRAVES (BASEBALL TEAM) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA120989-0085 </DOCNO>
