back Brian Lucas leaves La Quinta's Joe Slouka on the ground after a short 
gain. ; Photo, La Quinta quarterback Richard Weaver completes a pass despite 
pressure from Corona del Mar's Phil Holland. ; Photo, Sea King receiver Weston 
Johnson is hit by Jorge Sanchez, who was called for pass interference. 
