</P>
<P>
Verdugo's Mexican restaurant 
</P>
<P>
3850 S. Plaza Drive, Santa Ana. 
</P>
<P>
Salsa nightly. 
</P>
<P>
J.C. Fandango's 
</P>
<P>
1086 N. State College Blvd., 
</P>
<P>
Anaheim. 
</P>
<P>
Salsa six nights a week. 
</P>
<P>
These are among the more popular nightspots. Some have a cover charge. People 
interested should call ahead because schedules often change. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
